\id RUT  
\h Rut 
\toc1 Ruth 
\toc2 Rut 
\toc3 Rut 
\mt1 Rut  
\c 1  
\s1 Vuyowo kaiwae Elimelek na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® gara  
\p
\v 1 Va e mbaŇčako iyako, mbaŇčaniya giyagiya ghanji mbaŇča th…® mbaro, dagabora i yomara e vanautumako iyako t…®ne. Iya kaiwae amala regha rara Bet…®lehem, Juda e t…®ne, weiyaŇčgiya levo na le ŇčgaŇčga theghewo, th…® gara na wo veth…® yaku vanautuma regha idae Mowab na veth…® meghala vuyowoko iyako gheko.  
\v 2 Amalake idae Elimelek, levo idae Naomi\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Naomi gharumwaru ‚Äúwarari i riyevanjara‚ÄĚ.\f* na lenji ŇčgaŇčga theghewo, idaidanji Malon na Kiliyon. Thiye uu Eprat, th…® mena Bet…®lehem, Juda e t…®ne. Va th…® wa Mowab na mbowo veth…® yaku mbaŇča ubotu gheko.   
\p
\v 3 MbaŇča inanji gheko Elimelek i mare, na Naomi mbema ghamberegha eŇčge weiyaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčgama theghewoma.  
\v 4 Gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake va veth…® ghe gheko ‚ÄĒ th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Mowab wanakauniye theunyiwo. Eunda idae Opa na eunda idae Rut. Lenji yakuyaku gheko vama i wo Ňčgoreiya theghathegha hoyaworo,  
\v 5 na Malon na Kiliyon tembe th…® mareva. Naomi vambema ghamberegha eŇčge vara, le ŇčgaŇčgama kaero nandereŇčgi na le gh…®moru tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.   
\s1 Naomi na Rut th…® njogha Bet…®lehem  
\p
\v 6 MbaŇča Naomi amba ina Mowab e t…®ne, kaero i loŇčwa toto ghambae ghar…®ghar…®niye utuninji, \nd Giya Loi\nd*\f + \fr 1:6 \ft ‚Äú\+nd Giya Loi\+nd*‚ÄĚ ‚ÄĒ Utuutuke iyake gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye vaŇča lumo raŇča ‚ÄúYahweh‚ÄĚ o ‚Äúthe LORD‚ÄĚ\f* kaero i mwaewo weŇčgiya le bodaboda, na ghan…®Ňčga kaero veimaimava weŇčgi. Iya kaiwae Naomi na oyawanyiye th…® vivatha na th…® roiteta Mowab.  
\v 7 WeiyaŇčgiya oyawanyiyema theunyiwoma, Naomi i iteta ghembama va th…® yakumawe, i reŇča e kamwath…®ma iya i wa na ve raŇčgima Judiya.   
\p
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge e kamwath…® mborowae, amba Naomi i dage weŇčgiya oyawanyiyema iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi themiunyiwona hu njogha e ghambamina na hu yaku weimiyaŇčgiya lemi bodaboda. Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na ne ghare weŇčga Ňčgoreiya ghemi va gharemi weŇčgo na weŇčgiya thiyema vama th…® marema.  
\v 9 Na tembe ya naŇčgo weva \nd Giya Loi\nd* na ne i vakathaŇčga tembe hu lagheva na hu yaku weimiyaŇčgiya lemi gh…®mogh…®moru.‚ÄĚ  
\p Naomi i mwanambiyeŇčgi e ghareghare na i mwaewoŇčgi. Weinji lenji gharev…®r…® th…® randa na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye  
\v 10 na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThava Ňčgoreiyana! Weime eŇčge ghen na ra wa weŇčgiya len bodaboda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Ko iyemaeŇčge Naomi i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúOyawanyiŇčgu, mbema i thovuye moli vara hu njogha. Buda kaiwae nuwamiya weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi? Ne val…®kaiwae tembe ya ghamb…®Ňčgiva gh…®mogh…®moru, th…® thegha matuwo na tembe hu vaŇčguŇčgiva?  
\v 12 Mbema hu njogha eŇčge, oyawanyiŇčgu. Kaero yalagh…®sar…® moliya ghino na ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu tembe ya gheva. Na othembe thoŇčgo amba val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya vaidiya Ňčgama, na thoŇčgo ya ghena weiŇčgu lo gh…®moru gougouke noroke na ya vaidiya Ňčgama,  
\v 13 ne val…®kaiwae mbowo hu dageten…®Ňčga e ghe na wo hu roroghagha ghaghad th…® thegha matuwo? OyawanyiŇčgu, hu ghareghare iyake ma val…®kaiwae. Budakai va i yomara e ghino i maŇčga kivwala budakai i yomara weŇčga. Kaiwae Lo \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i roghereiye wanaŇčgo na vuyowoke iyake i lagh…®ye moli weŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Iyake i vakathaŇčgi na mbowo th…® randava. Amba Opa i mwanavatha yawanyiye e ghareghare na i ghawole, ko iyemaeŇčge Rut i thovuvu Naomi.   
\p
\v 15 Naomi i dagewa Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, len ghaghe kaero i njogha weŇčgiya le bodaboda na weŇčgiya le loi i kururu weŇčgi. Ghen tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, u njogha wein.‚ÄĚ \fig Wo u thuwe, len ghaghe kaero i njogha weŇčgiya le bodaboda|src="CO00956B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="1:15" \fig*   
\p
\v 16 Ko iyemaeŇčge Rut i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúThava u vavothaŇčaŇčgo na ya roiteteŇčge. Mbema u vatomwe eŇčge na weiŇčgu ghen. Ne the val…®vaŇčga u wawe, ya wawe, na ne the val…®vaŇčga vo yakuwe, va yakuwe. Len ghar…®ghar…® lo ghar…®ghar…®, na len Loi lo Loi.  
\v 17 The val…®vaŇčga vo marewe ne va marewe na th…® bekuŇčgowe. \nd Giya Loi\nd* le lith…® lagh…®ye moli e ghino thoŇčgo ya roiteteŇčge; ko mbe mare eŇčge vara ne i vakathainda ra meghaghath…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 MbaŇča Naomi i thuwa Rut le vothako, ma tembe i rovur…®ghegheva e variye njoghawe.   
\p
\v 19 Elaelama theunyiwoma kaero veth…® loloŇčgaova ghaghad veth…® vutha Bet…®lehem. MbaŇča th…® vutha, ghar…®ghar…® gharenji iyo kaiwanji na wanakau th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjora Naomi iya elagh…®niyeko?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava hu uno idaŇčgu Naomi, huŇča eŇčge ‚ÄėMara,‚Äô\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Mara gharumwaru ‚ÄúmaŇčgamaŇčganiye‚ÄĚ.\f* kaiwae Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye i vakatha yawaliŇčgu gham…®nae mbema maŇčga eŇčge.  
\v 21 Va ya roitetake lo bigibigi veimaima, ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgo kokowaŇčgu. Buda kaiwae hu uno idaŇčgu Warawarariniye, na mbaŇčake Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye kaero i roghereiye wanaŇčgo na ya vaidiya vuyowae!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Iyake i woraŇčgiya va ŇčgoroŇčga na Naomi i roiteta Mowab na i njogha Bet…®lehem weiye Rut t…®nan Mowab. E mbaŇčako iyako bali uloulo amba i wora eŇčge r…®ghe.   
\c 2  
\s1 Rut i kaiwo Bowas ele bali ghauma  
\p
\v 1 Amala regha ina Bet…®lehem, ina Naomi le gh…®moru Elimelek e ghauu t…®ne. Idae Bowas, na amalake iyake iye giya vwenyevwenye regha.   
\p
\v 2 Rut, iye t…®nan Mowab i dage weya Naomi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare u vatomweŇčgo na ya wa e umako t…®ne na va mbana bali iya rakakaiwoko th…® ten na th…® mban iteteko. The rakakaiwo ne ghare i njaweŇčgo na i varaeŇčna e ghino amba ya kaiwo e ghereiye.‚ÄĚ \fig Ya wa e umako t…®ne na va mbana bali iya rakakaiwoko th…® ten na th…® mban iteteko|src="co00961b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="2:2" \fig*  
\p Naomi i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa na vo vakatha Ňčgoreiye, yawanyiŇčgu.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Iya kaiwae Rut i wa e umako t…®ne, i rereghamba weŇčgiya rakakaiwoko, na i mbana baliko th…® roitetako e ghereinji. Rut va i minjanuwae, thela i wo Bowas, iye i mena Elimelek e ghauu t…®ne, iya le bali ghauma i kaiwokowe.   
\p
\v 4 Amba ma i mwelumweluŇčguya kaero Bowas i vutha, i ri Bet…®lehem. I Ňčaevair…®Ňčgiya le rakakaiwo iŇča, ‚ÄúWeimi \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewo e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Bowas i vaito le rakakaiwoko lenji randeviva iŇča, ‚ÄúElako tabwako i mena thela e ghauu t…®ne?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Rakakaiwoko lenji randeviva i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúIye t…®nan Mowab. Naomi va i njoghamake weiye, va th…® ri Mowab.  
\v 7 Me naŇčgo e ghino na ya vatomwewe i rereghamba weŇčgiya rakakaiwoko i mban…®mba reghamba bali rakakaiwoko th…® mban itete. Me kaiwo wa mbe mbaŇčambaŇča ghaghad mbaŇčake, na mbe mbaŇča ubotu eŇčge me roru e riburibuko na i towowe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Amba Bowas i dage weya Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúElana, wo u vandeŇčeŇčgo. Ne u ndewa e uma reghava na vo mbana baliwe, mbe u mban…®mba vara e umake iyake. Mbe u yaku vara gheke weinaŇčgiya wanakauke thiyake.  
\v 9 Mbe u njimbukiki wagiyawe vara kaiwoke iya e balike ghauma t…®ne, iya gh…®mogh…®moruko th…® kaiwowe, na u ghambuŇčgiya wanakauna iya th…® mban reŇčanawe. Kaero ma dage weŇčgiya iya gh…®mogh…®moruko na ne th…® ndevakatha vakatha vathar…® regha e ghen. Na thembaŇča ne mbwa i ghar…®Ňčge u wa na vo mun e mbwako varivariye iya gh…®mogh…®moruko meth…® gudurawe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Iyake kaiwae Rut i kururu na ghamwae ve thukumwa thelau, na i dage weya Bowas iŇča, ‚ÄúBudakai kaiwae na u rerenuwaŇča lagh…®ye kaiwaŇčgu? Budakai kaiwae na gharen weya ghawora loloniye?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Bowas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya loŇčwevao utuutunin na ŇčgoroŇčga len vakatha thovuye weya yawanyin…®ko mbaŇča len gh…®moru i mare iteteŇčge. Ya ghareghare va ŇčgoroŇčga na u roiteteŇčgiya rama na t…®na na ghembako iyava mad…®ban…®ko i dobuwe, na va ŇčgoroŇčga na u mena na kaero u yakuva ghar…®ghar…® mava mbaŇča regha u ghareghareŇčgi e t…®nenji.  
\v 12 Ya naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na ne i giya njogha e ghen len vakathako kaiwae. Na modoko iyako mbala veimaima na ndendewo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iye Isirel lenji Loi, na amalagh…®niye Ňčgoreiya ma, e vineiye raberabe kaero menda u mena na u vaidiya vwar…®vwar…®r…®we.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Rut i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhan thanavu mbema i thovuye vara e ghino, ghino ghen len rakakaiwo, amalana. Mo utu e ghal…®Ňča udauda i mwanavair…®Ňčgo, othembe len rakakaiwona wanakauko th…® lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 MbaŇča ghan…®Ňčga ghambaŇča, Bowas i dage weya Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena ra ghan…®Ňčga. U wo bred…®ke na u woutu e mbwake monyomonyoke.‚ÄĚ  
\p I yaku weiyaŇčgiya rakakaiwoko amba Bowas mbowo i giyava bali vwalavwala vavanawe. I ghan…®Ňčga na kaero val…®kaiwae, ko vavana vambe inawe.  
\v 15 MbaŇča Rut kaero me wao na ve mban…®mba bali, Bowas i rodage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwo gh…®mogh…®moruko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu viyathu na i mbana bali, othembe i mban Ňčgoreiya kaero yavayavathaŇčgiko, ne hu ndeguva utu omathaŇčaghad.  
\v 16 Mbala hu bigiraŇčgiya eŇčge bali vavana e mbambarana iya hu ten…®Ňčgina e t…®nenji, hu roitete na elagh…®niye i romban…®Ňčgi. Ko iyemaeŇčge ne hu ndedageten…®we.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Rut i mban…®mban…®vatha balima ghaghad varae ve ronja. MbaŇča i wo umbwa na i Ňčge baliko varivariye e wokiwokiyeko na i yaruvatha mbombouyeko, va i wo epa,\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Epa Ňčgoreiye 22 lita.\f* raŇča ghemidima vethethiŇčo Ňčgamwara.  
\v 18 Rut i biginjogha bali e ghemba, na i vatomwe weya yawanyiye ŇčgoroŇčga baliko le lagh…®lagh…®ye me mban. Na tembe i giya weva Naomi ghan…®Ňčgama me ghan…®varema.  
\v 19 Yawanyiye i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke aŇčga mo mbana bali? Thela ele bali ghauma mo kaiwowe? Ya naŇčgo na Loi mbala i mwaewo weya giyako iyako iya me thalavuŇčgena noroke.‚ÄĚ  
\p Rut i dage weya yawanyiye iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalako iya ma kaiwo ele umako t…®ne idae Bowas.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Naomi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa naŇčgo \nd Giya Loi\nd* iye ghare weŇčgiya thavala e yawayawalinji na ramaremare ma mbaŇča regha iko, i mwaewo weya amalako iyako.‚ÄĚ Na mbowo i gotubweva iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana iyena la boda regha na iye Ňčgoreiya ghanda rathalavu, val…®kaiwae ne i njimbukikinda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúNa tembe me dageva e ghino na iŇča, ‚ÄėMbe u mena u kakaiwo vara weinaŇčgiya lo rakakaiwoke ghaghad th…® uloulovao elo balike.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Naomi i dage weya yawanyiye Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, wou yawanyiŇčgu, mbala ma rakakaiwo e bali ghanji umauma vavana th…® mena th…® vakatha vuyowo e ghen, thoŇčgo kaero u wava e bali ghauma reghava. I thovuye moli mbe u kaiwo vara weinaŇčgiya wanakauna iya Bowas ele balina ghauma t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Iya kaiwae Rut mbe i kakaiwo vara e baliko ghauma t…®ne. Mbe ina vara rakakaiwoko wanakauko evasiwanji ghaghad th…® uloulovao bali na wit. Na Rut mbe i yaku vara weiye yawanyiye.   
\c 3  
\s1 Rut i naŇčgo weya Bowas na i thalavu elagh…®niye na Naomi  
\p
\v 1 Va mbaŇča regha amba Naomi i dage weya yawanyiye Rut iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ya tamweya kamwath…® na thoŇčgo val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya tuthiya gh…®moru regha na u vaŇčgu mbala len yakuyaku i thovuye na wein len warari.  
\v 2 U renuwaŇčakikiya Bowas, iya mendava vo kaiwo weinaŇčgiya le rakakaiwo wanakauma. Iye ghanda rathalavu la gh…®moru ghanjiuu loloniye.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft VaŇča lumo raŇča ‚Äúclansman redeemer‚ÄĚ.\f* Wo u vandeŇčeŇčgo. Noroke gougou ina balima ghaghamba vwaravwara i vwara balima na i ghetha varivariye na ndamwandamwa weiye mbombouye.  
\v 3 Iya kaiwae nuwaŇčguiya u thithu, u ghavatha na u worawa bunama e riwan. U njimbo kwama thovuye, amba u wa Ňčgora i vwaravwara na i ghetha balikowe, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ne inan gheko mbe u vakatha wagiyaweŇčge vara na thava i ghareghareŇčge ghaghad ne munumu na ghan…®Ňčga e ghereiye.  
\v 4 U njimbu vakatha mbaŇča ne ve ghena. Mbala u wa na vo ronja evasiwae, u livaira thogana e gheghena na u ghena evasiwae. Tene i dage e ghen ŇčgoroŇčga ne u vakatha na uŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Rut i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya mo utuŇčana.‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 Kaero Rut i wareri i wa e ghamba vwaravwara bali na i vakatha Ňčgoreiya yawanyiye me utumawe.   
\p
\v 7 MbaŇča Bowas i ghan…®vao na i mun…®vao, ghare i warari lagh…®ye. I wa Ňčgoreiya baliko ghawabwi ghadidiye na ve ghenawe. Rut tembe seiwo seiwo vara i wawe, i tatethara gheghe kaero i ghena.  
\v 8 Mbala vama i wo gougou mborowae, amba Bowas i raraghana ghare, i ghenevagh…®le na mara i wa e gheghe, ghare i yo mbaŇča i thuwa wevo eunda i ghena e gheghe. \fig Rut tembe seiwo seiwo vara i wawe, i tatethara gheghe kaero i ghena|src="Ruth3.1.tif" size="col" copy="LRec" ref="3:7" \fig*   
\p
\v 9 Bowas i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThela ghen?‚ÄĚ  
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Rut, len rakakaiwo. Kaiwae gh…®moruko va ya vaŇčgukaiko le boda ghen na ghen ghamarathalavu val…®kaiwae tembe u njimbukikiŇčgova.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Rut va iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema u vaŇčguŇčgo eŇčge.‚ÄĚ Ko iyemaeŇčge vaŇča Hibru iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema u livagumoŇčgo e ghan kwamana mbothiye e vwataŇčguke.‚ÄĚ\f*   
\p
\v 10 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na i mwaewo e ghen, elana. Ghan thanavuke iya u vakathake e ghino noroke i kivwala ghan thanavu iya u vakavakatha weya yawanyin…®na. Ma mo tamweya gh…®moru amba thegha ndamwandamwa na nuwaniya u vaŇčgu, othembe i vwenyevwenye o mbinyembinyeŇčgu?  
\v 11 Ko mbaŇčake, Rut, thava u gharelagh…®lagh…®, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako th…® ghareghare euriya ghen na ghino ne ya vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye kaiwan.  
\v 12 Emunjora ghino lo boda iya gh…®moruna va u vaŇčgukaina na mbaro iŇča ghino ya njimbukikiŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge gh…®moru regha yawanyin…®na le boda na iye ma i bwagabwaga moli e ghen Ňčgoreiya ghino.  
\v 13 Mbowo u yaku vara gheke gougouke iyake na ne mbaŇčambaŇča amba vara thuwe na ra vanamwe weinda. ThoŇčgo le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye na i varaeŇčna i njimbukikiŇčge, i thovuye; ko thoŇčgo ma le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye, ya dagerawe \nd Giya Loi\nd* e marae, ne ya wo vuyowoko iyako. Iya kaiwae u ghena vara gheke ghaghad ne igh…®viya.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Rut mbowo i ghena gheko ghaghad igh…®viya rakaraka, ko iyemaeŇčge va i thuweiru amba maramomouwo na mbala ma lolo regha i thuwe, kaiwae Bowas maŇča ma nuwaiya lolo regha i ghareghare mena gheko.   
\p
\v 15 Bowas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU liraŇčgiya ghan kwamana ghayaboyabo na u livamomoya gheke.‚ÄĚ I vakatha Ňčgoreiye, amba Bowas i liŇčgiya bali e t…®ne, le vuyovuyowo mbalavama 30 kilogram. I thalavu i th…®n…®vair…® amba amalagh…®niye i njogha e ghembako t…®ne.   
\p
\v 16 MbaŇča Rut i njoghama weya yawanyiye, kaero yawanyiye i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga me le vakatha e ghen, elana?‚ÄĚ  
\p Rut i utugiyavaowe bigibigiko wolagh…®ye Bowas me le vakathakowe.  
\v 17 I gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúNa balike i lagh…®ye moli Ňčgoreiye vara iyake me giya weŇčgo na iŇča thava ya njoghama e ghen kokowaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 Naomi i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúRut, tha u rerenuwaŇča, mbema u yaku eŇčge na u roroghagha ŇčgoroŇčga ne une ve yomara. Bowas mane i yaku noroke ghaghad ne ve vanamwe renuwaŇčana iyana.‚ÄĚ   
\c 4  
\s1 Bowas i vaŇčgu Rut  
\p
\v 1 Amba Bowas i wa Ňčgoreiye ghembako ghaghambaru, iye ghamba mevathavatha, na ve yakuwe. Amba Elimelek le bodama iya i roth…®gha amalagh…®niye, amalama Bowas me utuŇča utuniyema, i mena e ghadidiye, na Bowas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, wo u mena u yaku gheke.‚ÄĚ I wa iyena kaero ve ronja.   
\p
\v 2 Bowas i vaŇčguvathaŇčgiva ghembako gharandeviva theyaworo na veth…® yayaku gheko weinjiyaŇčgi.  
\v 3 Amba i dage weya le bodama iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Naomi kaero menda i njoghama Mowab e t…®ne, nuwaiya i vakuneŇča thelau vuvura, iya la bodama Elimelek va i mare itetema.  
\v 4 Ma renuwaŇča val…®kaiwae u ghareghareya iyake iya kaiwae ma womena renuwaŇča iyake e ghen. MbaŇčake iyake thoŇčgo nuwaniya u vamodonjogha randevivaŇčgike thiyake e maranji. Ko thoŇčgo ma nuwaniya, u woveŇčgoma len renuwaŇča, kaiwae vavamodonjogha ele val…®vaŇčga i viva moli ghen ko amba ghino.‚ÄĚ  
\p Amalama i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vamodonjogha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Ko amba Bowas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThe mbaŇča ne u vamodanjogha thelauko iyako, kaero Ňčgoreiye ne u vaŇčgwa Rut iye wambwi t…®nan Mowab na len wevo, na mbala hu ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai wein na thelauna iyena i yaku weŇčgiya ghembwiyena le ŇčgaŇčga.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Amalako i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Ňčgoreiyeva iyana, ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya la boda vakavakathaniye kaiwae ne i vakathaŇčge na iwaeŇčge lo ghamba mbaro ma i lagh…®ye. Ghen eŇčge u vamodonjogha; ghino ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Me vivako Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye me lenji vakatha Ňčgoreiyake mbaŇča meth…® vakuneŇča o th…® vegiya weŇčgiya bigibigi: ravavakune iye ne i bigiraŇčgiya gheghe ghae na i giya weya ravavamodo. Iyake va ghanji thanavu na i vaemunjoruŇča renuwaŇčako iyako kaero th…® vanamwe.   
\p
\v 8 Kaiwae Ňčgoreiyako, mbaŇča amalako iŇča, ‚ÄúU vamodanjogha,‚ÄĚ i bigiraŇčgiya gheghe ghae na i giya weya Bowas.   
\p
\v 9 Amba Bowas i dage weŇčgiya randevivaŇčgiko na thavalava va inanji gheko iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke taulagh…®na ghemi e marami kaero ne ya vamodonjogha bigibigiko wolagh…®ye weya Naomi; Elimelek le bigibigi na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Kiliyon na Malon lenji bigibigi.  
\v 10 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Rut iye t…®nan Mowab, Malon ghembwiye, iye kaero lo wevo. Iya kaiwae bigibigiko wolagh…®ye mbene i yaku wevara Malon le ŇčgaŇčga, na Elimelek gheuuko mbala mbe i mbuthumbuthu vara e ghabodako t…®nenji e ghambaeko. Ghemi ne hu utuŇča utuutuke iyake weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 RandevivaŇčgiko na vavanava th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, ghime wo thuwe na ne wo utuŇča. Wo naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na ne i vakatha wevona iyana, iya i mena e len Ňčgolona na nevole Ňčgoreiya Reitiyel na Leya, thiye wabwi Isirel ot…®nat…®nanji. Tembe wo naŇčgo weva \nd Giya Loi\nd* na mbala i vakathaŇčge na u vwenyevwenye uu Eprat e t…®ne na giya vwenyevwenye ghen Bet…®lehem e t…®ne.  
\v 12 \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i vakatha wevoko iyako na ne hu ghamba gamagai na ne th…® vakatha ghanuuna idae lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Peres gheuu, Juda na Tamar narinji.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Deivid orumburumbuye  
\p
\v 13 Iyako e ghereiye Bowas i vaŇčgwa Rut na levo. Bowas i ghenethaiya levo Rut na \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewowe i vaidiya Ňčgama. I ghamb…®kaiya Ňčgama gh…®moru.  
\v 14 Wanakau Bet…®lehem e t…®ne th…® dage weya Naomi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúTaulagh…®ke ghinda ra tarawe \nd Giya Loi\nd*, kaiwae kaero le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye na noroke rumbun Ňčgama gh…®moru, iye nevole i njimbukikiŇčge. Wo naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na Ňčgamana iyena nevole idae i lagh…®ye Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji.  
\v 15 Yawanyin na val…®ghareghare mbe ghare vara e ghen, na le vakathako iyako e ghen i kaitotowo, i kivwala wevo i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai gh…®mogh…®moru theghepir…®. Na kaero ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru kaiwan, na iye nevole i njimbukikiŇčge mbaŇča nevolema u yalagh…®sar…® moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Amba Naomi i wo Ňčgamako e n…®man…®maeko, i mwanambiye e ghareghare na mbe gharewe vara.  
\v 17 Wanakauko e ghembako iyako t…®ne th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNaomi kaero rumbuye Ňčgama gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ Th…® rena idae Obedi. Iye Jese ramae na Deivid ramaya Jese. \fig Naomi i wo Ňčgamako e n…®man…®maeko|src="co00975b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="4:16" \fig*   
\p
\v 18 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake Deivid orumburumbuye, i ri weya Peres i mena ghaghad Deivid:  
\b  
\li1 Peres nariya Hesron,   
\li1
\v 19 Hesron nariya Ram,  
\li1 Ram nariya Aminadab,   
\li1
\v 20 Aminadab nariya Nason,  
\li1 Nason nariya Salmon,   
\li1
\v 21 Salmon nariya Bowas,  
\li1 Bowas nariya Obedi,   
\li1
\v 22 Obedi nariya Jese,  
\li1 Jese nariya Deivid.   